com.google.gwt.gwtai.applet.client
Class AppletAccomplice

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.gwtai.applet.client.AppletAccomplice

public abstract class AppletAccomplice
extends java.lang.Object

This abstract class provides functionality that is only meant to be used within the GwtAI library. The information obtainable from a AppletAccomplice object are mainly used to build up the wrapper widget.

Author:
Adrian Buerki
